  <p class="ndx-walkthrough-step__screenshot-caption govuk-body-s">The Cognito login page where you enter your admin credentials</p>
</div>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">What you should see</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">
  After logging in, you should see the main dashboard with:
</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li>A navigation sidebar with "Document Translation" and "Simply Readable" sections</li>
  <li>The Document Translation history view (initially empty)</li>
  <li>Options for "Create Translation Job", "Quick Text", and "Quick Translate"</li>
</ul>

